{"tid":529862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[狂賀]【活動加劇】菲律賓馬榮火山瀕爆發 逾萬人急疏散","createTime":"2018-01-15T07:45:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-15T09:06:07.000Z","uid":65346,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"27a93fb7172a6018531d85e0e463bd39e71f9ea3","tid":529862,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:45:27.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180115/57709303\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180115%2F57709303&d=H04InM%2BlYy8Za4FUzunqCjA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=63389092\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180115%2F57709303&h=a9b24c4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180115/57709303</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n菲律賓呂宋島東南部著名旅遊景點馬榮火山（Mount Mayon）活動加劇，專家警告火山或在數天內爆發，逾萬人被迫離開家園。<br />\n<br />\n馬榮火山近日數度冒出蒸氣，過去24小時出現火山地震和落石；逾1.2萬人要離開方圓7公里的撤離區，當局警告或出現泥石流和有毒烟雲。<br />\n民防部門指居民留在撤離區有危險，並會吸入火山灰。「由於過去幾周連續降雨，火山山坡上堆積了泥濘，或導致出現火山泥流。如果降雨不停，可能會有危險」。<br />\n馬榮火山高2,460米，2014年曾有熔岩流出，當時有6.3萬人離開家園；專家估計今次的熔岩比2014年的流動性更高。"},{"pid":"cf56b96865e0942a37b53fdb1b2a1b4bc177b22c","tid":529862,"uid":65346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:47:13.000Z","msg":"距離香港約1401.68 公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa7002e269bf39e88118f73ea7e79148b0843ccc","tid":529862,"uid":118120,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起佢地總統笑笑口咁提香港人質事件 ,  <br />\n人地文化係幾時都鐘意笑笑口"},{"pid":"60975dd7ddd41b7e85d3f641f611d579e0864c9e","tid":529862,"uid":65346,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"fa7002e269bf39e88118f73ea7e79148b0843ccc","tid":529862,"uid":118120,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:48:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n諗起佢地總統笑笑口咁提香港人質事件 ,  <br />\n人地文化係幾時都鐘意笑笑口"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:49:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b11aa7c69f5ff4bd4c23c42c725bb12b9cf7b983","tid":529862,"uid":48,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/15/154940_aa5542cc811d1a81bf777eee723b2d77.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F15%2F154940_aa5542cc811d1a81bf777eee723b2d77.png&h=85fe0ed5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ebd2977a0effcc74361ed6d4b3fe47c6e6535dc7","tid":529862,"uid":62599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T08:55:24.000Z","msg":"我好憤怒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a5d2b1b5250bd35dccc21c361bfed90f5cdec4","tid":529862,"uid":43721,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf56b96865e0942a37b53fdb1b2a1b4bc177b22c","tid":529862,"uid":65346,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T07:47:13.000Z","msg":"距離香港約1401.68 公里<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-15T09:01:45.000Z","msg":"1401公里 + 1.2萬人 = 2012年<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\"